Job Details
we are looking for Arabic speaking Purchasing Executive  preferably Jordanian &  Syrians to handle a team of sales agent. Have ability to judge the current market scenario and take right decision at the right time. Negotiation Skills and ability to meet client’s needs, Knowledge of local market environment.
Requirement:
-With 3-5 years experience as a Sales Manager in lubricants field
-Proven track record and sales history
-Team Player
-Ready to work as a team
-Can handle pressure
Company Offer: -Attractive Salary -Full Admin support  If you are willing to join a dynamic team please send us your updated resume/CV with latest photo
